OL,3,CChancellor denies delaying infected
OL,4,Cblood compensation payouts
OL,6,FThe chancellor has denied delaying
OL,7,Fcompensation payments to victims of
OL,8,Fthe infected blood scandal, after
OL,9,Fnearly 120 MPs wrote to him demanding
OL,10,Fhe allocate funding for it in the
OL,11,FBudget on Wednesday.
OL,13,FJeremy Hunt insisted: "I am personally
OL,14,Fcommitted to paying victims of the
OL,15,Fcontaminated blood scandal as quickly
OL,16,Fas possible."
OL,18,F"I was the health secretary who set up
OL,19,Fthe inquiry, and I've given evidence
OL,20,Fto the inquiry twice", he said.
