OL,6,FHowever, Mr Hunt said compensation
OL,7,Fwould not be paid until the inquiry
OL,8,Finto the scandal had concluded.
OL,10,FThe chancellor says he's committed to
OL,11,Fdelivering compensation but not until
OL,12,Fafter the inquiry into the scandal has
OL,13,Fconcluded.
OL,15,FThe inquiry is due to finish on May 20
OL,16,F- but in April 2023, the chair of the
OL,17,Finquiry Sir Brian Langstaff,
OL,18,Frecommended a "compensation scheme
OL,19,Fshould be set up now and it should
OL,20,Fbegin this year."
