OL,6,FCabinet Office minister John Glen
OL,7,Freplied: "I think he will understand
OL,8,Fthat I can't pre-announce aspects of
OL,9,Fthe Budget, but the general point he
OL,10,Fis making about urgency is one that I
OL,11,Fhear, as I said to him when I met
OL,12,Fbefore the February recess."
